---
import SectionTitle from "@/components/common/SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="relative w-full py-12 px-5 md:px-32 overflow-hidden">
  <SectionTitle
    title="자기소개"
    subtitle="저를 소개합니다"
    titleKey="about.title"
    subtitleKey="about.subtitle"
  />

  <div
    class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-start gap-8 md:gap-[114px]"
  >
    <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex justify-center w-full md:w-auto">
      <div
        class="w-[200px] h-[275px] md:w-[302px] md:h-[415px] rounded-[15px] overflow-hidden border border-white/10"
      >
        <img
          src="/images/profile/preparing.svg"
          alt="정우진 프로필"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-white text-base md:text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-left"
        >
          <span data-i18n="about.greeting">안녕하세요👋</span><br />
          <span data-i18n="about.intro">
            저는 문제를 발견하고, 해결책을 제품으로 구현하는 과정을 즐기는
            개발자 정우진입니다.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4 md:mt-[20px]">
        <p
          class="text-white text-base md:text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-left"
        >
          <span
            class="text-[#EAB736] font-semibold"
            data-i18n="about.belief.highlight"
          >
            기술의 온기로 더 나은 세상을 설계한다
          </span>
          <span data-i18n-html="about.belief.rest">
            는 신념을 지니고,<br />
            사람을 이해하는 기술, 그리고 사회에 긍정적인 임팩트를 남기는 서비스를
            만드는 Startup Founder로 성장하고자 노력하고 있습니다.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 md:mt-[60px] flex justify-start w-full">
        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 md:gap-x-[40px] gap-y-4 md:gap-y-[25px]"
        >
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 md:gap-1 items-start">
            <span class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">17+</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-[#575757] text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold"
              data-i18n="about.stat.projects">완성된 프로젝트</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 md:gap-1 items-start">
            <span class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">19+</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-[#575757] text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold"
              data-i18n="about.stat.tech">다루는 기술스택</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 md:gap-1 items-start">
            <span class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold">1</span>
            <span
              class="text-[#575757] text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold"
              data-i18n="about.stat.awards">수상경력</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5 md:gap-1 items-start">
            <span class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold"
              >1720+</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-[#575757] text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold"
              data-i18n="about.stat.github">GitHub 기여도</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
